Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier  而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.27,0:00:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.54,0:00:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.18,0:00:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角  追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.68,0:00:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.55,0:00:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.23,0:00:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.17,0:00:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.77,0:00:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.37,0:00:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.68,0:00:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.34,0:00:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.91,0:01:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.32,0:01:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.92,0:01:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.52,0:01:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.79,0:01:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.39,0:01:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.03,0:01:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.76,0:01:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.27,0:01:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.09,0:01:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞成這副模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.92,0:01:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不像你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.26,0:01:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我無話可說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.96,0:01:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用實戰培養新人的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.70,0:01:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來還是太勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.24,0:01:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把記憶換到電子腦裏面行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.21,0:01:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,矢野不會再生嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.21,0:02:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像GHOST無法複製
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.24,0:02:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以就算複製記憶  GHOST還是不會寄宿其中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.62,0:02:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果只考慮維持9課的運作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.92,0:02:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們或許不需要新的人才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.09,0:02:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是考慮今後的情勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.99,0:02:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們不得不克服的課題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.83,0:02:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  這次作戰還是不要安排阿東
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.37,0:02:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.40,0:02:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請好好照顧他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.44,0:02:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.62,0:02:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#20  北端的混迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.00,0:02:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.33,0:02:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的老朋友給的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.50,0:03:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經確認前俄軍軍官  現在改行做黑手黨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.94,0:03:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波利斯·賈布羅夫和他的數名部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.77,0:03:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從該國運送鈽元素進入擇捉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也就是說久世那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.15,0:03:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算去買那批鈽元素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.59,0:03:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想用核武器武裝自己  宣佈成為獨立國家嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.46,0:03:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再大膽也要有個限度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.40,0:03:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臥底偵查的諜報員被他的義體人同伴殺害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以致他們現在行蹤不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.71,0:03:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諜報員被殺是2小時前啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.54,0:03:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.71,0:03:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話雖然這麼說  我們其實已經沒有選擇餘地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.75,0:03:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.92,0:03:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼  我們怎麼特定地點呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.83,0:03:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡亂跑去擇捉也不會有結果的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.06,0:04:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公安部給的情報裏面似乎有提示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.13,0:04:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說擇捉市的佐川電子公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.47,0:04:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未經許可就擴建Berutarube區的地下工廠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.47,0:04:09.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Berutarube：位於擇捉南端的舊型電腦都市，也是擇捉的中心都市\N現在是多國企業與國際犯罪組織間利益關係複雜的巢穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Berutarube？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.77,0:04:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有俄國潛水艇基地的那個地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.21,0:04:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,記得俄軍撤退的時候  已經炸毀埋起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.61,0:04:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.78,0:04:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐川的擴建工程如果順利的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.55,0:04:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在應該已經挖到那個基地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.15,0:04:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此  真的很可疑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.99,0:04:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潛水艇基地的話  拿來藏偽裝船最合適
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.99,0:04:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是沒有確切證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.10,0:04:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假設他們有在計劃那麼大的交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.30,0:04:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當地的情報販子應該也會掌握到什麼才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.14,0:04:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長  我們就這樣進入擇捉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.91,0:04:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了以防萬一  請要求海上保安廳封鎖出島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果難民拿到核武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.08,0:04:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼  所有的枷鎖都會解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.25,0:04:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.62,0:04:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  我相信你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.59,0:05:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候如果不能抓到久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.96,0:05:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內廳的行為就會消失在黑暗當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍方也將介入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.43,0:05:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能讓出島成為戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.20,0:05:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.64,0:05:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來沒有任何陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.28,0:05:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離交易還有一些時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.51,0:05:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們輪班休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.31,0:05:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了\N知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.79,0:05:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  要不要吃點這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.30,0:05:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.94,0:05:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好難吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.78,0:05:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,味道真的很糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.61,0:05:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得跟課長抗議才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一些時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.85,0:06:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要檢查一下電子腦活性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.75,0:06:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.69,0:06:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是對久世妄想的規模感到有點迷惑罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.33,0:06:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不懂你的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.86,0:06:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他到底有什麼樣的妄想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.30,0:06:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直截了當說的話  可以算是征服世界吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.80,0:06:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.37,0:06:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是無藥可救的誇大妄想狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.47,0:06:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  你竟然會被那種東西迷惑\N一點都不像你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.77,0:06:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直就像思春期的小鬼\N遇到命中注定對象的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.11,0:06:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  這樣一切就清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.62,0:06:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然個別的11人病毒在他身上發作過一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.59,0:06:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是他原本擁有的資質和思想產生了目前的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.06,0:06:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妄想本身確實很老套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.76,0:06:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  我們不能一笑置之的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.77,0:06:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是真心想要當上獨裁者來促成世界和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有這種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.57,0:07:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且腎上腺素的分泌已經達到正常人會死亡的量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們應該認定久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.85,0:07:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經進入聖域了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.85,0:07:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖域是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.79,0:07:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是已經變成傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.56,0:07:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從歷史上來看  這種人可以發揮難以置信的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.89,0:07:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,例如"切·格瓦拉（古巴革命）"\N"麥康姆·X（黑人人權運動者）"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.03,0:07:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"卡西爾斯·克雷（拳王阿里）"就是這一類人的典型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.77,0:07:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟希特勒不同嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.70,0:07:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然某種意義上是同類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.40,0:07:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  思想上比較接近的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.07,0:07:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是「甘地」和「金恩博士」吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.74,0:07:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,常常跟他連線的難民們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.01,0:07:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,借由裝有劃分和過濾裝置的網絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.15,0:07:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沉醉在他現場轉播的行為當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.52,0:07:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  他之所以不加上偏見也不打算共享意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.19,0:07:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因為他知道過了他的GHOST界線就是危險區域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.39,0:07:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說我那時也很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.93,0:07:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種話一點都不有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.06,0:08:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川、帕茲、波瑪待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.10,0:08:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備交易地點錯誤時的支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.43,0:08:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.10,0:09:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧  軍國主義者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.37,0:09:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是危險的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.61,0:09:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然已經返還
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.44,0:09:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  俄國人和日本人的摩擦不會馬上就消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.42,0:09:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建設中的地下空洞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.86,0:09:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能穿過這裏到達基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.93,0:09:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許就能跟久世見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.03,0:09:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我們有那個運氣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.50,0:09:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果沒有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.44,0:09:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候只能跟佐川的工程人員直接面對面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.77,0:09:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒多餘時間等少校的聯絡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.02,0:10:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.52,0:10:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽說要買武器  所以上了這艘船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.29,0:10:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  如果知道是你指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕不會到這裏來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.93,0:10:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.20,0:10:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你不必勉強在這裏陪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.40,0:10:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以就這樣回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.04,0:10:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者消失在擇捉的街頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.21,0:10:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會強迫你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.61,0:10:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也贊成革命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.78,0:10:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是最早教我們何謂革命的是「傳說」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.95,0:10:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在出島大部分的人都知道「久世同志」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.98,0:10:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是幾乎沒有人知道你的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.49,0:10:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我不服氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.06,0:10:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到現在還是遵照「傳說」的指導\N有自爆的覺悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.47,0:10:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種做法只是自我滿足而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.40,0:10:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,革命是要有GHOST才會產生的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.74,0:10:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我想知道你的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.91,0:10:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也給我能夠相信你的根據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.89,0:11:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.07,0:11:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天我們要拿到手的武器是鈽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.37,0:11:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要用那個逼日本政府承認出島是獨立國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.18,0:11:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欠的東西要確實還清\N這是最低限度的規則不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,懂了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挺威風的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.26,0:11:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有什麼可以借給別人的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.86,0:11:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是大姐頭嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.79,0:11:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還記得我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.66,0:11:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說克氯丹還在這裏面做生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.60,0:11:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.80,0:11:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那當然是真的  請這邊走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.71,0:12:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是非常謹慎呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.75,0:12:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別客氣  請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.42,0:12:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托古薩  你在這裏等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.89,0:12:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請這邊走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.42,0:12:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也到這裏就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.52,0:12:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這個世界太慇勤會惹人厭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.57,0:12:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.40,0:12:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟大姐頭一起工作很辛苦對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是不跟大姐頭打好關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.77,0:12:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會後悔莫及的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.69,0:12:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克氯丹  是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.69,0:12:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根室登陸作戰的時候  承蒙你照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.43,0:13:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻性防壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛才被燒死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潛入哪裏被燒死的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像還在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.57,0:13:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  能燒死克氯丹這種程度的黑客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.77,0:13:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,技術相當高明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.77,0:13:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻性防壁的運作方式也是機密保持法所不允許的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.35,0:13:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.99,0:13:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,磁碟片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.32,0:13:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然用這麼舊的東西當外部記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.83,0:14:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛那傢伙花了那麼多功夫  就為了刪除這個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.60,0:14:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐川的秘密帳簿嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.47,0:14:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出貨  檸檬蛋糕20公斤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.67,0:14:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,檸檬蛋糕？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.11,0:14:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每公斤50萬美金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.74,0:14:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,M退出Au的交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.15,0:14:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仲介商  佐川K
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.22,0:14:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,B.J.\N檸檬蛋糕20公斤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.89,0:14:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,K抽成40％＝退休金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.42,0:14:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,買家\NB.P.介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正如我所猜測的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.23,0:14:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他正在竊取鈽的交易情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.90,0:14:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐川的K
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.30,0:14:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,K是北端特務課長加賀崎嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.54,0:14:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他擔任仲介買賣每公斤50萬美金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.07,0:14:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賣家是波利斯·賈布羅夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.71,0:14:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,買家是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.65,0:14:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ASIAN／B．P.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是指亞洲難民…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說…剛剛的黑客是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.72,0:15:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加賀崎抽成的部分已經改成日元了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.79,0:15:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經把頭款匯給佐川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.56,0:15:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2億4千萬日元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.17,0:15:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民從哪裏拿到這麼一大筆錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.90,0:15:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世準備的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.47,0:15:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是的話  他是怎麼辦到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  幫了我大忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.31,0:15:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還記得你說過佐川電子\N是你最討厭的日系企業啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.96,0:15:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不應該辭掉報道廳的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.26,0:15:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話  內廳說不定會是個比較好一點的機構
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.23,0:15:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川  交易地點在核潛艇基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.50,0:15:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個案子也有可能跟內廳有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.27,0:15:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.37,0:15:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.21,0:15:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特他們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.18,0:15:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經在地底深處了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.84,0:15:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通訊受到阻隔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.48,0:15:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我馬上過去那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.59,0:16:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間差不多到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.96,0:16:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.43,0:16:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再告訴我一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.43,0:16:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽說買鈽至少要25萬美金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.24,0:16:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這筆錢你要怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.27,0:16:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從俄國人手上騙過來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.37,0:16:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是  我會老實付錢買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.48,0:16:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了讓國民理解我們的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.11,0:16:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錢是我請一直消費難民的國民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.45,0:16:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點一點「捐」出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這樣說你大概聽不懂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.35,0:16:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,整個設計是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.66,0:16:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在那些對自己的豐衣足食\N毫無自覺的國民總儲蓄額
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.56,0:16:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很輕鬆就超過900兆日元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.16,0:16:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實他們對這個數字也毫無自覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.70,0:16:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後你知道這些儲蓄的利息當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.54,0:17:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一筆表面上不存在的金額嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.58,0:17:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,表面上不存在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.38,0:17:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是一日元以下的金額
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.82,0:17:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終端機資料上通常也沒有顯示的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.72,0:17:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小數點以下的數字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.26,0:17:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要從網絡上的帳戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.62,0:17:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,徵收這微薄幾分錢的金額
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.29,0:17:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一天就有數千萬計的金額
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.56,0:17:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我設計程序把這些錢匯進我的銀行戶頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.30,0:17:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錢就是從那裏來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.37,0:17:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一般人根本不知道自己的帳戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.31,0:17:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有小數點以下的存款
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.75,0:17:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀行現在都把帳戶管理交給AI
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.48,0:17:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民在這個國家工作明明就要預先扣稅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.49,0:17:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻完全不允許歸化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.76,0:17:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國民還是我行我素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.46,0:17:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全沒注意到系統做了多嚴重的壓榨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.43,0:17:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只攝取著順口又容易接受的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.20,0:18:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這真是一個欺瞞的社會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.80,0:18:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想讓大家知道這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.87,0:18:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那筆錢現在到底有多少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.71,0:18:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.55,0:18:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,107億6千萬吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.95,0:18:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是我們的革命所能用的軍事資金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.22,0:18:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.35,0:18:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.22,0:18:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是一個恐怖分子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.79,0:18:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.56,0:18:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在有點醉心於英雄主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你留下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.54,0:18:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓船準備好隨時可以出航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.68,0:18:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.89,0:18:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是有問題的擴建區域嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.86,0:18:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.93,0:19:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天到底怎麼搞的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.16,0:19:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們應該有得到許可吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是現場的負貴人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.63,0:19:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  你剛剛說「又來了」對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.83,0:19:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.04,0:19:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不久前來了2台母公司的武裝機甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.87,0:19:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再之前是一個俄國的奇怪義體人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.51,0:19:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提著兩個大皮箱下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.31,0:19:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中獎了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.08,0:19:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.11,0:19:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是為什麼陸上自衛隊也來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.07,0:19:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼只有你一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.84,0:19:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賈布羅夫與加賀崎都被公安盯上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.34,0:19:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我一個人來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.98,0:19:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點完成交易吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.96,0:20:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.86,0:20:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是指定帳戶的匯款記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.46,0:20:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿去確認吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.08,0:20:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.98,0:20:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們等一下馬上過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.73,0:20:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交易成立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.66,0:20:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彼此都一樣無法確認內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.17,0:21:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,丟下武器出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.67,0:21:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以違反兵器管製法和非法交易核物質的罪名逮捕你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.88,0:21:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點給我看你的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.91,0:22:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齋藤  有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.94,0:22:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要管這裏  快去抓柯伊爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.94,0:22:04.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯伊爾·克拉斯諾夫：俄國戰鬥型義體人，鈦制義手支架延伸至肩胛骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.55,0:22:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.32,0:22:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.25,0:22:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.89,0:22:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要確實破壞掉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.16,0:22:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我站住  久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.93,0:22:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那個放到地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.84,0:22:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不立刻開槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.61,0:22:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你知道這是什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.55,0:22:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.41,0:22:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的獵物是你的人頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.95,0:22:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那恐怕很困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.12,0:22:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點把皮箱拿到船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.39,0:22:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…\N快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.06,0:22:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你瞧不起我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.58,0:23:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我體內行星和星星的銀河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.28,0:23:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著它們每一個都唱著同樣寧靜的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.86,0:23:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在現實當中從來沒看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.83,0:23:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣美麗的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.16,0:23:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有一點懷疑或恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.70,0:23:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到一個聲音—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.77,0:23:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到一個聲音呼喚我的名字—然後現出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.31,0:23:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我省視自身—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.58,0:23:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光隨時都圍繞著我—時間已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.68,0:23:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相  所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.05,0:23:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去讓這一切成真的—它就在裏面
